## License

This software is licensed under the MIT License. However, please note that this project uses [Npcap](https://npcap.com), a proprietary packet capture and injection library.

### Npcap Usage

This software requires Npcap to function. Npcap is free for personal and limited commercial use on up to five systems. For more than five systems, or for redistribution, a [Npcap OEM License](https://npcap.com/oem/) is required. Users will need to download and install Npcap manually from [Npcap's website](https://npcap.com/#download).

Please refer to the [Npcap license](https://github.com/nmap/npcap/blob/master/LICENSE) for more details.

